sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Go Server
    participant DS as Datastore

    Note over B,S: Quiz Load
    B->>S: GET /api/v1/survey/promotion/{slug}
    S->>DS: FindBySlug
    DS-->>S: Promotion config
    S-->>B: {active, name, slug}
    B->>S: GET /api/v1/survey/questions
    S->>DS: FetchQuestionConfig
    DS-->>S: Age groups + product mappings
    S-->>B: Questions config
    B->>S: GET /api/v1/survey/stores
    S->>DS: ListActiveStores
    DS-->>S: Store list
    S-->>B: {stores[]}

    Note over B,S: Quiz Completion
    B->>S: POST /api/v1/survey/customer
    S->>DS: SaveSubmission
    DS-->>S: Submission ID
    S-->>B: {submissionId}
    B->>S: POST /api/v1/survey/updatestore
    S->>DS: UpdateSubmission store
    S-->>B: 200 OK

    Note over B,S: Email Dispatch
    B->>S: POST /api/v1/survey/email
    S->>DS: RenderAndSave email HTML
    S->>DS: SaveEmailRecord
    S-->>B: 200 OK
